title: Lifted Masks

description: LibriVox recording of Lifted Masks, by Susan Glaspell. Read by Arielle Lipshaw. In this collection of short stories, Susan Glaspell examines the unique character of America and its people. (Summary by wildemoose) For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording.
